This is the moment a baker lost both his legs as the shop front of his bakery came crashing down on him.

Josiah Pereira dos Santos, 48, was crushed by the facade of his own shop in Goiania, Brazil, on Saturday morning.

Security cameras inside the shop show Mr dos Santos standing outside the bakery.

